{"tid":1609700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偽勇武同和理非同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:09:07.000Z","uid":128348,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5beeb5f339c5bec517f2adb3a23a98867b4bd0ad","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"認真 你地比少少心理準備好唔好<br />\n<br />\n依家出去唔你9fing fing 就算<br />\n<br />\n唔係食過tg 就叫勇武<br />\n<br />\n勇武係一個idea 一個心態<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔夠覺悟 唔該轉下職<br />\n<br />\n幫手scout 下收下風 睇下水 都對前線好大幫助<br />\n<br />\n至於和理非<br />\n<br />\n你出到尼唔係淨係9 企 比你地圍住吹水<br />\n<br />\n唔該都幫手睇水（ 唔係叫你淨係望住前面， 係叫你幫手睇下橫街 其他有機會包既路線）<br />\n<br />\n前線幫你頂子彈 你幫手set下rb等d 狗包抄得冇咁快<br />\n<br />\n都唔係好過份既要求 下話<br />\n<br />\n前線唔單止需要你地既聲援 <br />\n<br />\n更需要你地身體力行去幫<br />\n<br />\n好多時候前線都一腳踢 但面對住愈尼愈多前線比人捉<br />\n<br />\n你唔係咁都唔肯幫呀？"},{"pid":"6917104c932d667299b4597957865f7dd269443f","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6f3cf6fbed985244f9fb57ac3c17f988cad6e81","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"唔逐幫幫手"},{"pid":"98c2cb86d4933b5d76f5bb82dba6a1b2ee1e0f9e","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de83b6bcc551a39631ebab722e999f1c0c492dc3","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"改善呀 屌"},{"pid":"966faa48e09391e4586c476121ddcac70358b743","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"你唔幫就輸"},{"pid":"d51d40920cb2d0335860a51246558ce228a41e50","tid":1609700,"uid":294052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"偽勇武都好 同我一人一磚"},{"pid":"5f5486a61cf940536e0cc752828e15b74ba8d2ac","tid":1609700,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"